Mango Banana Smoothie🍠🍌🍒 follow (@deliciousfoodvideos)
💛
Recipe by: @secretsquirrelfood
1 cup mango
1 banana
1/2 cup almond milk
1/4 tsp cinnamon
4 ice cubes
1/3 cup pomegranate seeds
Blend everything except for the ice and pomegranate seeds for 1 minute. Add ice and blend again. In a separate glass, add pomegranate seeds and smash it up. Carefully pour the mango smoothie in the glass and enjoy!! 💖
